name: Secondary Time of Use Service (Schedule STOU)
description:
Applicable to electric power service supplied at
secondary voltage. Not applicable to standby or resale
service.

This rate schedule is subject to all applicable Electric
Adjustments as on file and in effect in this tariff.
energycomments: Adjustments = Earnings Share adjustment + Demand Side Management Cost adjustment + Purchased Capacity Cost adjustment + Transmission Cost adjustment + Electric Commodity adjustment + Clean Air-Clean Jobs Act rider + Renewable Energy Standard adjustment
